-- Peugeot Has Invested $960 Million in Peugeot 508 Model, La Tribune Reports
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-09-07T04:19:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-07/peugeot-has-invested-960-million-in-peugeot-508-model-la-tribune-reports.html

          
          
             PSA Peugeot Citroen has invested
about 750 million euros in its Peugeot 508 model, La Tribune
reported, citing the company.  
 Peugeot plans to build 200,000 508s in 2012, of which
60,000 will be made in China, the newspaper said.  
          
          


  


        